UniAdmin
========
Uni Admin is a simple administration layout support for ruby on rails web application. Now it includes:

* an admin base controller and dashboard action
* a simple admin layout
* a simple admin CSS file
* an integrated admin menu
* a record list table style

View the demo.gif in the plugin category.

Installation
========
script/plugin install http://ruby-on-rails-plugin-uni-admin.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/uni_admin

Add routes:
map.connect '/uni_admin/', :controller => 'uni_admin', :action => 'dashboard'
map.connect '/uni_admin/demo', :controller => 'uni_admin', :action => 'demo'

Example
=======
* After installation, start your server: >script/server
* Visit http://localhost:3000/uni_admin/
* Visit http://localhost:3000/uni_admin/demo

